import { Header } from './components/Header'
import { Main } from './components/Main'
import { ContextFunction } from './context'
import { Theme } from './components/Theme'

function App() {
    return (
        <ContextFunction>
            <Theme>
                <Header />
                <Main />
            </Theme>
        </ContextFunction>
    )
}

export default App
